13/01/2004
SOFIA, Bulgaria -- President Georgi Parvanov signed a decree appointing Colonel Kircho Kirov to the post of Director of the National Intelligence Service (NIS), the presidential press service said Monday (12 January). 
Kirov was also promoted to Brigadier General. 
He has been acting NIS Director since last February, replacing General Dimo Gyaurov. 
(BTA, BNT - 12/01/04)
